    public interface NamedInteraction<T extends Participant>
extends Interaction<T>
    A named interaction is an interaction having a fullname and aliases in addition to a shortname. The fullname is the description of the interaction. Aliases would be synonyms of the interaction.
    Since:
    13/11/13
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
